## Anti-Patterns

### Don't Do This

| ‚ùå Anti-Pattern                       | Why Bad                            | ‚úÖ Instead                      |
| ------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| Copy-paste without reading            | Miss bugs, don't learn             | Read, understand, then use      |
| Ask AI to "fix" without understanding | Won't learn the fix                | Ask "why is this broken?" first |
| Use AI for everything                 | Lose fundamental skills            | Practice basics without AI      |
| Skip tests because AI said it works   | AI doesn't test your edge cases    | Always test AI code             |
| Trust AI on security                  | AI can suggest vulnerable patterns | Verify against OWASP, docs      |

